column5: I also asked this on the fishing reports site. Any heads up on Nestor Falls area recent fishing. Going up next week, Thanks
Just got back on August 30th. Fishing was decent, caught fish in 3.5' - 24', fish were on steep drop offs with current seemed to be the best. We did most of our fishing past Sand Bay.
Was there algae bloom there on the 30th. That green slime. Stuff?
Ya, it was all over the lake.
